**Digital preservation** refers to the task of ensuring that "digital information of continuing value remains accessible and usable"^[[Digital preservation](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Digital_preservation).].
In particular, a lot of the information on the internet depends on other online resources through referencing and hyperlinking.

